channel.title: A way to check if ur server is online?
channel.description:
I'm not sure if i port-forwarded correctly or don't even know what my real problem is....my friend and i spend a lot of time getting his variables set and he gets no error message like"couldn't find path specified" but it still says error connecting to server.
long story short, how do i know for sure my server is online to other people. :|
